{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e86c097e31","title":"关于原林办工作人员处理问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bbd0cb8a04","index":0,"year":1975,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"e86c097e31"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"96fd1cf4c6","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林办，指林彪办公室。"},{"id":"0d91e3bce5","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是对蒋葆生1975年6月24日来信的批语。信中说，我是一个共产党员，原系北京医院医生，“九一三”事件前被组织派往林彪处做保健工作。“九一三”事件后，组织上决定我参加学习班，集中学习，到现在已近4年，而我的问题如同其他学员一样，至今仍未作出正式结论。当前，全国正遵照您的指示，认真落实政策，我感到十分鼓舞，渴望自己也能早日回到原工作单位，为党、为人民做一点有益的工作。同时，也希望其他学员同志的问题能够得到妥善的解决。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fa771d0a38","type":"title","text":"关于原林办工作人员处理问题的批语P","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"},{"id":"96fd1cf4c6","type":"paragraph","text":"中央：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"},{"id":"0d91e3bce5","type":"paragraph","text":"林办各下级人员，责任较轻，不宜久在学习班。似宜早作结论，免予追究，分配工作，以观后效","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"},{"id":"e95e9bbb1d","type":"paragraph","text":"请讨论决定。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"},{"id":"84ef9a042a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"},{"id":"c5b232b50d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七五年六月三十日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31"}],"page":{"id":"34141b2216","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"e86c097e31","start":39,"end":39}}